185923CB.Line7.10BCF2: It wants ancient offerings returned. Offerings of devotion. Offering from those once worthy.

1DB93678.Line13.10BCF2: Then… then the Grinning One may speak to you, too!

3FD57A09.Line5.10BCF2: The dust showed me a labyrinth. Winding walls, endless halls. Laughing from the deep.

45358CB6.Line11.10BCF2: You brave the shadows. Bring what was lost to Ogai.

6751D047.Line3.10BCF2: But first… I must be proven. The Grinning One must see Ogai is worthy.

8ECE2685.Line1.10BCF2: It gnaws at me. So close. So close to its gifts!

B787FC14.VoiceDir3.10BCF2: trying to calm self, breathing between words

F0DCCD8D.Line9.10BCF2: But… Ogai is not made for demons and darkness. No, no…
